import React from 'react';
import { Form, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Input = ({}) => (
    <Container>
        <Form className='container col-sm-3 mt-5'>
            <Form.Group>
                <Form.Control 
                    type='text' 
                    placeholder='Type a message...'
                />
            </Form.Group>
    </Form>
     <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
         Submit
    </Button>
    </Container>
)

export default Input;
